parameters: Acknowledged. \c[27]【H Event】\c[0] The proposed amount is \V[47] mon.
承知する【提示金額　\V[47]文】\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

Hehe, I'm happy! This place is too conspicuous, let's go
over there in the shadows\I[15]

--The prostitution client pulled Karin by the hand into the
shadows.
Sure. I'll pay extra, so make sure you entertain me well.

--As a result of the negotiation, the price became
\c[17]\V[47] mon\c[0]!
I don't mind. You're quite sexy, after all. I'll pay more.

--As a result of the negotiation, the price became
\c[17]\V[47] mon\c[0]!

...Hmm. I can't pay any more than this. See ya. (The man
shook his head and walked away--)

Hey! Martial law is in effect right now. Return to your
homes. If you're attacked by demons, we won't take
responsibility, understand?

...It seems I can't go inside looking like this. Let's go
back in front of my house and change into my usual clothes.
Lady, I've come for a night visit again today.

No, we can't! I told you we shouldn't meet again, didn't I?!
Adultery is a capital offense...! If my husband finds
out...! Ah...nngh...\I[15]
(...Hm? Is there someone in the back of the park...?)

Hehe... Lately, there haven't been any officials around,
making our job a breeze.

Ah, totally, brother. Today we hit the jackpot with three
successful burglaries♪
(They seem to be burglars... What should I do...)
What the!? Are you the pursuers!?

A girl...? No, what's a girl doing alone at this hour... A
prostitute, perhaps...?
Hmm...? Haven't we met somewhere before!?

No! This is the first time we've met! (I remember now! He
was the burglar next to that glittering thief!)

Tch! Walking around at this hour of the night... Since
you've seen us, can't be helped. If you let us go, we'll
give you 500 mon.

...What are you going to use that stolen money for?
Depending on your answer, I might let you go.
Huh? What we're going to use the money for?

Pfft! Obviously, it's for our own sake! You think we're
playing Robin Hood, handing out money like Mouse Kozo?
Ridiculous!

What's with that look? Here, take the 500 mon and go home
quietly. Don't talk about us to anyone, got it?

...I don't need such a paltry sum as 500 mon. I'll turn both
of you in to the magistrate's office.

What did you say!? You think you can beat us brothers, you
night bird!?

Come on. If you underestimate me, you'll end up hurting more
than you'd expect!?

You've got some strange confidence... Let's be cautious.
Take this!
--The men threw a round object at Karin!
Don't dodge, knock it down \c[27][H Event]\c[0]
避けずに叩き落とす\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

--Kyaaah!? What, what is this!? It's all sticky...!? Could
it be...!

By the time you realize it, it's too late! The inside is
sticky rice! As you can see, it's super effective!

Phew... I finally got the sticky rice off. What a terrible
day it's been...

...What happened, Karin? With that look, were you attacked
by someone?
Y-Yugiri-chan? I-I'm fine! Just tripped a little...! Ahaha!

Be careful at night. You never know where evil spirits might
be lurking. See you, Karin--
--Karin bid farewell to Yugiri and left the scene.
Hmph! Such a pathetic attack, you think it would hit me!?

You'll curse your misfortune for meeting me in the dead of
night. Goodnight♪

Guhah! What a swift chop...! I can't dodge it!
Collapsing...!
--The two burglars were defeated by Karin!

...Now, I've caught the burglars, but what should I do? If I
take them to the magistrate's office, will I be suspected
too?

What's this? I heard voices while on my night patrol... Who
are these men, Karin? They're not demons, are they?

Perfect timing, Yugiri-chan! These men seem to be burglars.
Can you take them to the magistrate's office?

Hmm. Understood. We will take them. You did well to catch
them, Karin.

--The burglar brothers were taken away by Yugiri and her
companions.
(I'm somehow exhausted... I'll go home and sleep tonight)
